{"tid":1791360,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"仆你個街 去完個christmas party俾人炒撚左","createTime":"2019-12-20T17:29:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-21T03:16:55.000Z","uid":43557,"like":23,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"75f24f262e8c3853c8ce7d71ea83a2449825a77b","tid":1791360,"uid":43557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T17:29:18.000Z","msg":"今日收工公司搞christmas party<br />\n咁事先都講定每人要準備一份唔可以少過200蚊既禮物<br />\n咁我份人不嬲度開 緊係話撚之你啦<br />\n是但係屋企拎支未用過既洗頭水算<br />\n又重又大份<br />\n點撚之頭先抽果陣 原來老細都準備左份諗住一齊抽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我已經嚇撚到手震<br />\n跟住到我果份俾人抽 <br />\n仆你個街 真係抽中左老細<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢平時戴開假髮 其實冇頭髮 不過同事個個都扮唔知<br />\n佢一打開份禮物 全場靜撚晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我果刻已經想搵窿捐 <br />\n跟住佢問呢份禮物係邊個準備？<br />\n我果陣緊扮唔係自己冇出聲<br />\n點知有條仆街爆響口：我認得喇 份野我好似見住阿chris拎出黎架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n跟住成晚都冇乜人講野<br />\n老細臨走叫左我入佢房叫我唔洗再返<br />\n<br />\n而家唔知點同老母講 返左一個禮拜都唔夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3f57b5f77488fd169731742a4786d56a0ad45eb","tid":1791360,"uid":120627,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T17:34:09.000Z","msg":"太假 重作"},{"pid":"f0574aa6adb0632066577d8a21acda018e168a69","tid":1791360,"uid":317247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T17:48:15.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"5665b47b0028349955d315e41451ce6c46281ccc","tid":1791360,"uid":100550,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T17:50:16.000Z","msg":"1/10 <br />\n呀婆都知係潮文"},{"pid":"e45470bf2409618ac80d92ed6ba67a325f0b73d5","tid":1791360,"uid":5455,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T19:13:07.000Z","msg":"晴報記者又要上黎作文"},{"pid":"7651dfd988bb7ee96ac3f99a42877a13f239543c","tid":1791360,"uid":157261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T02:46:57.000Z","msg":"0/10"},{"pid":"e53210c68cce4be8e5fff6530cefa14c7b17f34e","tid":1791360,"uid":200034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T03:16:55.000Z","msg":"同老細入房無甜<br />\n0分重作"}]}